Subject: [PATCH 514/895] rpmsg: Move helper for finding rpmsg devices to core

Extract and move the helper function for finding rpmsg child devices to
the core.

Signed-off-by: Bjorn Andersson <bjorn.andersson@linaro.org>
(cherry picked from commit 8b881c07cb805e1a126d434359706e45864ea2df)
---
